<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-09-13T13:05:26-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-09-13T13:05:26-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-13T13:05:26-04:00</updated><title> Keurig 被发现对其咖啡包做出“不准确”的回收声明</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Keurig&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JUKChEWF3aubRXzthrGSTCL1X94=/0x1:5194x3464/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/ 73583734/2154292697.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Smith Collection/Gado/Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;4AbDKD&quot;>;Keurig 关于其一次性产品的可回收性做出了“不准确的陈述”根据美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 的说法，咖啡包。该公司同意发出停止令，并支付 150 万美元的民事罚款来解决指控。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id= &quot;VE1xV2&quot;>;&lt;q>;企业回收声明可能具有误导性&lt;/q>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;hgGasn&quot;>;这是一个有用的提醒，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/2022/10/24/23420689/ Plastic-recycling-us-greenpeace-report&quot;>;许多企业回收声明可能具有误导性&lt;/a>;。某些类型的塑料比其他类型的塑料更难回收。即使某些东西据称是可回收的，如果市政回收计划不接受该类型的塑料，它最终也可能被扔进垃圾桶。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;kYmsAy&quot;>;对 Keurig Dr Pepper Inc. 的指控源于其 2019 年和 2020 年年度报告称，该公司测试并“验证 [d] [K-Cup pods]...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2024/9/13/24243806/keurig-recycling-coffee-pods-sec-charges-settlement&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243806/keurig-recycling-coffee-pods-sec-charges-settlement" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243806/keurig-recycling-coffee-pods-sec-charges-settlement</id><author><name>贾斯汀·卡尔玛</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-13T12:55:45-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-13T12:55:45-04:00</updated><title>这个形状怪异、金丝雀黄色的东西是特斯拉的机器人出租车吗？</title><content type="html"> &lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/r8c8dd_0vAKTQprgefSZIOsr9EQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73583681 /acastro_180430_1777_tesla_0003.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;9Akukm&quot;>;一张严重伪装的车辆在华纳兄弟电影院周围行驶的模糊照片。昨晚，电影制片厂地块浮出水面，引发人们猜测它是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/3/24234785/tesla-robotaxi-event-warner-bros-mapping-data-musk&quot; >;传说中的特斯拉机器人出租车&lt;/a>;将于下个月揭晓。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;2eGVgU&quot;>;由于它的金丝雀黄色包裹和明显被操纵的形状，仅仅从这次目击中很难收集到更多关于机器人出租车的信息。关于这张照片的一切都应该持保留态度，包括轮胎、四四方方的后端、奇怪的车顶凸起 (&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/7/24151497/tesla-激光雷达-luminar-elon-musk-sensor-autonomous&quot;>;激光雷达？&lt;/a>;），以及扰乱引擎盖凹痕。一切并不像看上去的那样。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;pzRgQ7&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://electrek.co/2024/09/13/tesla-is-testing-a-goofy-camouflaged-robotaxi-prototype-ahead-of -reveal/&quot;>;据 &lt;em>;Electrek&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 报道，这张照片首先由 u/boopitysmopp 发布到 Reddit，据说他是华纳兄弟的一名员工（该帖子已被已删除，并且 Reddit 用户已删除其个人资料，因此...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243807/tesla-robotaxi-间谍射击-reddit-yellow-camo-shape&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243807/tesla-robotaxi-spy-shot-reddit-yellow-camo-shape" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243807/tesla-robotaxi-spy-shot-reddit-yellow-camo-shape</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-13T11:46:44-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-13T11:46:44-04:00</updated><title> TIFF 2024：来自多伦多的所有最新电影评论</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;2024 年多伦多国际电影节将于 2024 年 9 月 3 日在安大略省多伦多举行，TIFF 灯箱外可见 TIFF 徽标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/FTvbEhVxh1kWPeQook7Uadp7RCk=/0x0:8500x5667/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73570557/2170074383.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption >;摄影：Mathew Tsang / Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;定期更新我们看到的所有内容。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2024/9/7/24235914/tiff-2024-toronto-movie-reviews-trailers&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/7/24235914/tiff-2024-toronto-movie-reviews-trailers" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/7/24235914/tiff-2024-toronto-movie-reviews-trailers</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-13T11:45:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-13T11:45:00-04:00</updated><title>我刚才到底看到了什么？</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;电影《Megalopolis》中的静态图像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/bMbws24maX6kmVdlMAZqdCp014E=/0x0:900x600/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73583528/Megalopolis_Still_01.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：狮门影业&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;弗朗西斯·福特·科波拉 (Francis Ford Coppola) 酝酿已久的史诗《大都市》是一系列松散联系的想法，与未煮熟的世界和令人尴尬的对话联系在一起。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24243766/megalopolis-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24243766/megalopolis-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24243766/megalopolis-review</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-13T11:17:12-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-13T11:17:12-04:00</updated><title> Spotify 正在测试一种新方法，让儿童歌曲不再出现在你的收听历史记录中</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Spotify 徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-8pYHlLEzZO7I4GdBvu1ccWeYHk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73583473/STK088_SPOTIFY_CVIRGINIA_D.0.jpg&quot; / >; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;spuQLH&quot;>;如果孩子们要求重复听 &lt;em>;Encanto&lt;/em>; 的一首歌曲，它可以过滤回到家长 Spotify 个人资料的算法和建议。该公司尝试通过 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2019/10/30/20938076/spotify-kids-app-announced-disney-taylor-swift-family-plan&quot;>; 解决该问题专门的儿童应用程序&lt;/a>;，去年，Spotify 添加了一项功能 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/2/8/23591289/spotify-exclude-from-your-taste- profile-playlist-made-for-you&quot;>;从用户的品味配置文件中排除特定播放列表&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;6Tjw8V&quot;>;现在，&lt;a href=&quot;https://newsroom.spotify .com/2024-09-13/spotify-pilots-new-music-experience-for-young-listeners-on-family-plans/&quot;>;Spotify 正在三个国家/地区启动试点&lt;/a>;，以测试管理帐户的13 岁以下的用户。&lt;/p>; &lt;blockquote>;&lt;p id=&quot;0kWCAX&quot;>;对于父母和监护人来说，托管帐户使他们能够通过应用内控件（例如管理）更好地定制向年轻听众提供的内容&lt;a href=&quot;https://newsroom.spotify.com/2022-04-08/spotify-takes-discovery-to-the-next-level-in-a-new-beta-test/&quot;>; 的播放画布&lt;/a>;、视频和标记为露骨的内容。他们现在还可以决定年轻听众是否可以播放某些艺术家或曲目...&lt;/p>;&lt;/blockquote>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 9/13/24243778/spotify-management-account-parent-child-account-controls&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243778/spotify-managed-account-parent-child-account-controls" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243778/spotify-management-account-parent-child-account-controls</id><author><name>理查德·劳勒</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-13T10:47:04-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-13T10:47:04-04:00</updated><title> OnePlus Watch 2 是我们精选的 Android 智能手表之一，现已达到最优惠价格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;红皮书上 OnePlus Watch 2 的特写&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/lFEArrv7c64kSdJGfzWQdC7Q8N0=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73583407/247069_Oneplus_watch_2_AKrales_0125.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;除了提供 70 美元折扣外，OnePlus 还提供免费表带或充电底座供您选择。 &lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hdM4g2&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239115/google-pixel-watch-3- review-smartwatch-wear-os-wearable&quot;>;Google Pixel Watch 3&lt;/a>; 现已上市，而新款 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24236958/apple-watch-series-10-hands -on-bigger-brighter-and-thinner&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 10&lt;/a>; 即将上市，但并不适合所有人。幸运的是，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23449363/best-android-smartwatches-wear-os&quot;>;市场上有各种各样的优秀 Android 智能手表&lt;/a>;，今天，我们的最爱之一 - &lt;strong>;OnePlus Watch 2&lt;/strong>; - 将于 9 月 22 日以历史最低价 229.99 美元（折扣 70 美元）&lt;a href=&quot;https://onepluscom.pxf.io/ c/482924/916678/12532?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oneplus.com%2Fus%2Fbuy-oneplus-watch-2&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; >;直接来自 OnePlus&lt;/a>;。要获得优惠，您必须剪下优惠券，点击“查看所有优惠”然后“领取”即可找到优惠券。 OnePlus 还提供免费的 OnePlus Watch 2 表带（价值高达 39.99 美元）或 OnePlus Watch 2 充电底座（原价 29.99 美元）供您选择。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;olpHaP&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;在哪里预订 Apple Watch Series 10 和黑色 Apple Watch Ultra 2&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series- 10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;现在最值得购买的健身追踪器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com /22985108/best-fitness-tracker&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;7FkdYH&quot;>;如果您正在寻找 Wear OS 替代品&lt;a href= &quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239115/google-pixel-watch-3-review-smartwatch-wear-os-wearable&quot;>;Pixel Watch 3&lt;/a>; 或 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/23818557/samsung-galaxy-watch-6-review-bezels-smartwatch-wearables&quot;>;三星 Galaxy Watch 6 Classic&lt;/a>;，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24242856/oneplus-watch-2-ember-mug-2-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24242856/oneplus-watch-2-ember-mug-2-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24242856/oneplus-watch-2-ember-mug-2-deal-sale</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-13T10:46:55-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-13T10:46:55-04:00</updated><title> Astro Bot 听起来和玩起来一样棒</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Astro 机器人的屏幕截图，其中 Astro 骑着 DualSense 控制器在美丽的海洋上航行&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hDSk3qwqQHLs6OcTpd7Ezi5rrd4=/146x0:1496x900/1310x873/cdn .vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73583405/53971042042_e76709bbf9_h.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Team Asobi / Sony&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;AyTF66&quot;>;&lt;em >;Astro Bot &lt;/em>;是一款游戏&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237778/astro-bot-review-ps5-game-of-the-year&quot;>;我忍不住要传播福音&lt;/a>;，对其可爱的角色、明亮多变的关卡设计以及短暂而密集的 8-10 小时运行时间赞不绝口。但也许给游戏带来欢乐的最大因素是它的声音设计，这使得 Astro Bot 不仅能够吸引和愉悦您的思想，还能吸引您的身体。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id= “yfk2Tb&quot;>;&lt;em>;Astro Bot&lt;/em>; 在游戏开始之前就让我着迷了。我让 PS5 在游戏的预加载屏幕上运行，平静的铃声让我感到平静，同时也因为这首歌传达了一种迫在眉睫的奇迹而兴奋不已。这听起来就像是儿童电影开头的片段，让你知道一场冒险即将来临。音乐有...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243763/astro-bot-sound-design-dualsense-controller&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243763/astro-bot-sound-design-dualsense-controller" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243763/astro-bot-sound-design-dualsense-controller</id><author><name>阿什·帕里什</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-13T10:40:26-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-13T10:40:26-04:00</updated><title>所有新款 iPhone 16 机型之间的纸面比较</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;iPhone 16 Pro 手机四种颜色的并排特写。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/duw6WliC9dEUPC1xqpMGXmjTImk=/137x0:2438x1534/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73583397/iphone_16_pro.0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple 的高端 iPhone 采用钛金属表面和新的“沙漠”选项。 （这只是意味着暗金色。）&lt;/em>; |截图：苹果&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;PlsZlZ&quot;>;苹果新款&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237940/iphone-16-hands-on-pictures-price- features-apple&quot;>;iPhone 16&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237940/iphone-16-hands-on-pictures-price-features-apple&quot;>;16 Plus&lt;/ a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239802/iphone-16-pro-max-hands-on-apple-photos-features-price&quot;>;16 Pro&lt;/a>; 和 &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239802/iphone-16-pro-max-hands-on-apple-photos-features-price&quot;>;16 Pro Max&lt;/a>; 已经&lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/24237057/apple-iphone-16-plus-pro-max-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;>;在 9 月 20 日首次亮相之前接受预订&lt;/a>; 。距离 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24237714/apple-intelligence-generative-ai-features-update-schedule&quot;>;Apple Intelligence 还需要几周时间不过，人工智能功能已经到来，苹果将在 10 月份的 iOS 18.1 测试版中提供这些功能。但是，如果还没有那些大肆宣传的软件功能，那么第一天还有什么值得兴奋的呢？好吧，为了理解所有四种型号，我们进行了一些并排比较，概述了它们之间的一些关键差异（如果您非常倾向于自己制作 iPhone 16）。&lt;/p >; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;cMrPFT&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot; :[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;苹果 iPhone 16 活动：8 个最大的公告&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239739/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-watch-series- 10-airpods&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;这是您预订新款 iPhone 16 所需了解的所有信息&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237057/apple-iphone-16-plus -pro-max-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;iPhone 16 将作为正在进行中的作品发货&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2024/9/10/24241043/apple-iphone-16-pro-intelligence-ai-missing&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;9vVDow&quot;>;Apple Intelligence 将（最终）适用于所有四款新手机，每款手机都配备了苹果最新的处理器和新的相机控制...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /24242170/iphone-16-vs-pro-plus-max-comparison-specs-price-apple&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24242170/iphone-16-vs-pro-plus-max-comparison-specs-price-apple" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24242170/iphone-16-vs-pro-plus-max-comparison-specs-price-apple</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-13T10:35:02-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-13T10:35:02-04:00</updated><title>美国提出新的进口规则提案瞄准Shein和Temu</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;美国国会大厦照片的照片拼贴，背后有宪法图像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/R6yY_dOeYFhWDwdh7eMl3jnSuJk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73583389/STK481_STK432_CONGRESS_GOVERNMENT_CI VRGINIA_C.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge； Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;cydVLH&quot;>;拜登政府正在解决“最低限度”豁免问题，称一些中国电子商务公司“滥用”向美国客户运送价格低于 800 美元的产品关税。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;thchjQ&quot;>;新&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2024/09/13/fact-sheet-biden-harris-政府宣布采取新行动，通过打击含有不安全不公平贸易产品的最低限度运输来保护美国消费者、工人和企业/&quot;>;拟议规则周五&lt;/a>;将对来自中国的某些货物进行更严格的检查和关税——此举将影响 Shein 和 Temu 等超低成本零售商销售的产品。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c- float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;Q5DAI1&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;一次奇怪的短暂旅程穿越 Shein 的世界&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23970758/shein-forever-21-pop-up-new-york-fast-fashion&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt; /aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;7BzJMq&quot;>;随着 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnbc.com/2024/07/29/temu-shein-soaring-popularity-could-hit- amazon-meta-ebay-earnings.html&quot;>;Shein 和 Temu 等中国电子商务网站的崛起&lt;/a>;，美国要求免税的发货量激增。十年间，这些出货量从每年 1.4 亿件增加到超过 10 亿件，其中“大多数”使用豁免的产品来自中国。 Shein 和 Temu 声称获得豁免，因为他们发送单独的产品...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243653/us-biden-shein- import-rules-de-minimis-loop-hole&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243653/us-biden-shein-import-rules-de-minimis-loop-hole" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/13/24243653/us-biden-shein-import-rules-de-minimis-loop-hole</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-13T10:17:34-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-13T10:17:34-04:00</updated><title> Nightbitch 里面的狗还不够多</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;女人脸部的特写，上面有轻微的泥土污迹。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/GUlioGmzFQJSKFihtbxSPa8xURE=/0x228:4050x2928/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73583353/Nightbitch_KA_27x40_150dpi_V1_TypeV 2simple_CROP_rgb.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Annapurna&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;玛丽埃尔·海勒 (Marielle Heller) 的改编作品摆脱了书中凶猛的陌生感，转而采用一种更古怪、感觉良好的氛围。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24241246/nightbitch-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24241246/nightbitch-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24241246/nightbitch-review</id><author><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry></feed>